**Overview**

This dashboard provides information about the Analytical events collected by the Microsoft DNS Server integration.

These events provide detailed diagnostic information useful for in-depth analysis and troubleshooting of the DNS server operations. They are primarily intended for developers or advanced users interested in the internal behavior of the DNS service.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/microsoft_dnsserver/overview)
